Claw Code Query Engine: How the AI Agent Orchestrates Conversations
The claw code query engine is the stateful conversation orchestrator at the heart of the agent harness. It manages turn limits, token budgets, streaming output, message compaction, and session persistence — ensuring that multi-turn AI coding sessions remain coherent, efficient, and recoverable.

