Claw Code MCP Integration: Model Context Protocol Support
The claw code framework provides first-class support for the Model Context Protocol (MCP) — a standard protocol for connecting AI agents to external tools and data sources. MCP integration spans 6 transport types, deterministic tool naming, OAuth authentication, and multi-source configuration discovery.

